query:
/*+ NoMergeJoin(a1 q1 s t1 tq1 u1 b) */ select acc.location,
count(*)
from tag_question AS tq1
inner join question AS q1
on q1.id = tq1.question_id AND q1.view_count >= 100 AND q1.view_count <= 100000
inner join tag AS t1
on t1.id = tq1.tag_id AND t1.name IN ('book-recommendation',
'gparted',
'order-theory')
inner join site AS s
on s.site_id = t1.site_id AND s.site_id = q1.site_id AND s.site_id = tq1.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('askubuntu',
'math')
inner join so_user AS u1
on s.site_id = u1.site_id AND u1.upvotes >= 10 AND u1.upvotes <= 1000000
inner join answer AS a1
on s.site_id = a1.site_id AND a1.owner_user_id = u1.id AND q1.id = a1.question_id
inner join badge AS b
on s.site_id = b.site_id AND b.user_id = u1.id AND b.name IN ('Altruist',
'Benefactor',
'Electorate',
'Fanatic',
'Generalist',
'Quorum',
'Self-Learner',
'Steward',
'Suffrage',
'Taxonomist',
'Vox Populi')
inner join account AS acc
on acc.id = u1.account_id group by acc.location order by count(*) desc LIMIT 100;
